text: Émile Léon Fisseux was an archer from France. He was born on 15 February 1868. Fisseux competed at the 1900 Summer Olympics and the 1908 Summer Olympics.Émile FisseuxEmile FISSEUX == References == Category:1868 births Category:Year of death missing Category:French archers Category:Olympic bronze medalists for France Category:Sportspeople from Paris
